== About ==
This tool do 4 point calibration of evtouch device.
Originally based on calibrator from http://linux.chapter7.ch/touchkit/.

Features:
 * Read events directly from device
 * Don't require restart Xorg in special mode

Supported hardware:
 * GeneralTouch
 * ATouch
 * Digital Vision

== Build ==

=== With HAL ==
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

== Without HAL ==
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DDISABLE_HAL ..
make
